号称YouTube浏览量超过10亿次的英语VTuber“Filian”到底是什么？积极基于VRChat进行开发https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-filian/井文 Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:01:15 +0000 VTuberFilian https://www.moguravr.com/?p=249664 <p>在英语国家工作的Vtuber“ Filian”正在引起很多关注。 Filian是一名VTUBER，于2021年首次亮相，主要是在YouTube和Twitch上。撰写本文时的YouTube注册人数为25 […]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-filian/">YouTube邮政的英语“ Filian”是什么，它具有超过10亿次观看次数？基于VRCHAT的积极开发的活动</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>在英语国家工作的Vtuber“ <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/filian" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Filian</a> ”正在引起很多关注。 Filian是一名VTUBER，于2021年首次亮相，主要是在YouTube和Twitch上。在撰写本文时，YouTube注册人的数量已超过250万。</p><p>到目前为止，日本的认可还不是那么高，但是自2024年以来，它的受欢迎程度逐渐增长。谁是菲利安的话题？在本文中，我将介绍从“开始”到现在的步骤。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> （ <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://thevtuberawards.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=docs&amp;ust=1712913605508161&amp;usg=AOvVaw0-Y7qwgD7d7P55C3FRcagr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">引用2023年VTUBER奖</a>）</p><h2>我们正在使用vrchat进行活动</h2><p>Filian是基于社会VR“ VRCHAT”的VTUBER。已经实施了各种项目，例如在VRCHAT的游戏世界中玩，与其他玩家互动，并制作一个故事视频，以使粉丝感到惊讶。它的特征是一个可爱的人物，它在飞行或弹跳时会积极地使用整个身体行动。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="VRC物理学由Pro解释" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SEVJCulO0nw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="如果我大便，视频结束了" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kxgbtpUjPXA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1024x542.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1024x542.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-300x159.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-768x407.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1536x813.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="542" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-249661" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.i